rComments: Need good basic in economics to understand him. He is very helpful in the sense that he tries hard to clarify your questions if he understands them. He follows the text book very closely, his tests are on material he teaches in class, not the book material that he doesn't cover. This is his first year teaching, so his tests are fairly easy.
WELL I WOULD GUESS HE TRIED TO MAKE US UNDERSTAND WHAT HE WAS TALKING ABOUT, BUT HIS ENGLISH AND WAY OF TEACHING MAKE HIM THE TOUGHEST PROFESSOR FOR ME SO FAR.
